high_descs: Turn to the right and then left. Turn left and face the counter on the right.
Pick up the cup from the counter, behind the lettuce on the left.
Hold the cup and turn to the left, then left again. Turn and face the sink on the right.
Place the cup in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the cup, full of water.
Carry the cup and turn around. Turn left to find the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the cup inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Fill a cup with water and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Hang a left around the kitchen island to reach the heads of lettuce on the kitchen counter.
Pick up the black cup next to the heads of lettuce on the countertop.
Make a left around the kitchen island to head to the sink.
Fill the cup with water in the sink.
Walk around the island to the other corner of the room to reach the microwave.
Set the cup with water in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Fill a cup with water and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk around the kitchen island, then veer left to the counter with the two heads of lettuce on it.
Pick up the cup on the counter.
Turn around and go to the right of the kitchen island, walking to the sink.
Fill up the cup with water in the sink.
Turn left and walk straight to the wall, then turn left and walk straight to the microwave.
Place the cup in the microwave to the left of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup of water in a microwave.
